We start off

\begin{align*}
        & \min_{\boldsymbol{h},\boldsymbol{s}} \hspace{0.2cm} y(\boldsymbol{h},\boldsymbol{s}) \\
        & \text{ s.t. } \sum_{t=1}^{T} c_{h}h_{t} + c_{s}s_{t} \leq C \\
        & \hspace{0.82cm} h_t, s_t \geq B \hspace{0.2cm} \forall t \in \{1, ..., T\}
\end{align*}

